com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.restInterface
Class ServerRestResponseHandler

java.lang.Object
  com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.restInterface.ServerRestResponseHandler

public class ServerRestResponseHandler
extends java.lang.Object

Handles the responses from REST requests that ServerRestRequestTask makes. Handling includes providing user feedback (for failure or success), parsing and validating data by using the appropriate utility class(es), and sometimes even performing post-response data filtering using geocoding and geolocation distance calculations using the SimpleGeocoder class.

Author:
Nikos Moumoulidis
